# When Will I Be Famous?

Trying out the famous engine.

## Installation

```
npm install
```

## Development

Run the dev server with ```npm run dev```

Now the dev server should be running on localhost:1618

Run the linters with ```npm run lint```

Run All Tests with ```npm test```
